name: bodystocking
description:
其实我不太知道连体丝袜怎么翻译 如果有知情的朋友 麻烦评论告知 我好作修改

本Lora采用26张图片进行训练 各种学习率默认1e-4 1e-4 1e-5就行

epoch可以拉长点没关系 关键的训练分辨率拉到1024×1024

触发词OPP(可有可无) tag里加bodysuit,pantyhose,see-through等效果明显一点

推荐模型：perfectworldv2(真人模型也行 二次元模型好像脸会崩 这个我没深入测试)

推荐权重：0.3—0.7

Actually, I don't really know how to describe the clothes in the picture.

If you know, please comment and let me know.

This Lora uses 26 images for training.

lr=1e-4 unet_lr=1e-4 text_encoder_lr=1e-5

epoch≥20

resulotion=1024,1024

prompt：OPP,bodysuit,pantyhose,see-through

Recommended model：perfectworldv2(Realistic models are also effective.But anime model is not very good)

Recommended weight：0.3—0.7
